{"TopicId":11805,"ForumId":16,"TopicTitle":"Clearing space junk?","CreatedByName":"andromeda","CreatedById":776,"CreatedDateTime":"2012-06-01T06:01:07Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"andromeda","CreatedById":776,"CreatedDateTime":"2012-06-01T06:01:07Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EHi, I was wondering if there is anyway to remove the space junk off the map or start a new game because it\\\u0027s incredibly annoying \u0026gt;\u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_sad.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:(\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Awaras","CreatedById":15671,"CreatedDateTime":"2012-06-01T06:09:42Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EGo to Settings -\u0026gt; Gameplay and under \\\u0027System\\\u0027 set the \\\u0027Max persistent debris\\\u0027 slider to zero.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EIf you want to \\\u0027start a new game\\\u0027, just delete the \\\u0027persistent.sfs\\\u0027 file located in *your ksp folder*/saves/default\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"andromeda","CreatedById":776,"CreatedDateTime":"2012-06-01T06:14:24Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EThank you for your help \u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E)\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"silent_prtoagonist","CreatedById":1927,"CreatedDateTime":"2012-06-01T07:40:27Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EAlso, if you want to remove specific debris, you can go in and edit the persistent.sfs file (it\\\u0027s just a text file)\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Steve5451","CreatedById":18812,"CreatedDateTime":"2012-06-01T07:43:47Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EOr blast it out of the sky with the laser cannon. \u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cheesy.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:D\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"StellarUniverse","CreatedById":6629,"CreatedDateTime":"2012-06-02T17:46:11Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EI have made a mod called FL-C2000 tank!\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"sal_vager","CreatedById":16426,"CreatedDateTime":"2012-06-02T18:02:22Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E[mod]That\u0027s very nice StellarUniverse, I\u0027m sure you are proud \u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E But this thread is for ideas for clearing space junk, not mods.[/mod]\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}